            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Cartula de Franciano. In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Millesimo
                        centesimo vicesimo primo, mense martio, anno ab incarnatione eius,
                        indictione quarta Xa. Constat me <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/96">Ildebrandum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitem</rs>, filium <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/97">Raineri <rs key="#Count"
                                >comitis</rs>, qui Malabranca vocabatur</persName>, qui professus
                        sum vivere <rs key="#Roman">lege Romana</rs> et <persName key="#Countess"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/98">Maximilla</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> et <rs key="#Countess">comitissam</rs>
                        <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/99">Lupam</persName>, filiam
                            <persName>Soffredi</persName>, relictam <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/100">Malagalie</persName>, que
                        professa sum, propter legem patris mei, <rs key="#Lombard">legem vivere
                            Longobardorum</rs>, ipso namque Ildebrando mihi consentiente, in mundio
                        cuius permanere volo, presens presentibus in Dei nomine dixisse: “Vita et
                        mors in manu Dei est et melius est homini metu mortis vivere, quam spe
                        vivendi morte subitanea pervenire”. Ideo nos recordantes animarum nostrorum
                        parentum atque <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> Malagalie, nec non nostrarum,
                        ut dominus peccata nostra minuere dignetur, donamus atque igitur concedimus
                        atque offerimus nec non tradimus Deo et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78"
                            >Sancti Quirici</orgName> de <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/86">Populonio</placeName>, idest
                        medietatem de omnibus <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, cultis et
                        incultis, agrestis, aquis aquarumque decursibus, et <rs
                            key="#Saltworks #Sea_salt">salinis</rs>, quas vos <rs
                            key="#Littera/mandatum">recipistis et tenuistis</rs> olim per comitem
                        Rainerium et a <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/101"
                            >Adalasia</persName> in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Saltworks #Salt #Sea_salt #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/85"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> de
                                <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89"
                            >Franciano</placeName></geogName>, etiam medietatem de ipso <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellare</rs>, idest medietatem de omnibus terris
                        nostris, quam vos olim habuistis et tenuistis vel alii per vos, que sunt
                        inter hos fines: nam <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89"
                            >Petralata</placeName> est ex una parte et <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89">Cornachini</placeName> et
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89" key="#Rivers"><rs
                                key="#Rivers">rivus</rs> Pertuli</placeName> currit in <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89"><rs key="#Rivers"
                                >Notulo</rs></placeName> et Notulo vadit in <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89" key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                ><rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">stagno</rs></placeName>, ex
                        altera parte est terra <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/79">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> de <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/85"
                            >Monteviridi</placeName> et <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries">Sancte Marie Grasse </orgName>et
                        tenet secus stagnum et usque in Notulum. Quas autem res istas una cum
                        accessione et ingressione, omnia in integrum sicut supra legitur, ego
                        prefatus comes Ildebrandus et comitissa Maximilla et comitissa Lupa una cum
                        nostris heredibus tibi domino Dei gratia <persName key="#Abbots"
                            >Mauro</persName> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> damus atque
                        tradimus, ut tu et successores tui faciatis inde proprietario iure nomine
                        quicquid volueritis sine omni nostra nostrorumque heredum contradictione;
                        etiam promitto ego prefatus comes et Maximilla comitissa et Lupa comitissa
                        una cum nostris heredibus tibi Mauro venerabili abbati tuisque successoribus
                        prefatas terras defendere ab omni homine, quid si facere non potuerimus aut
                        si prefatas terras vobis tollere vel minuere voluerimus quovis ingenio,
                        promittimus eas vobis prefato abbati et tuis successoribus restituere in
                        duplum sicut pro tempore fuerint meliorate aut valuerint sub estimatione in
                        consimilibus locis, quia inter nos taliter convenimus. Actum in <geogName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/86"><placeName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/91"
                            >Cornino</placeName></geogName>, in <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/87"
                            >Suvereto</placeName>. Signa manuum […] comitis Ildebrandi et Maximille
                        comitisse et Lupe comitisse, qui queve hanc cartula qualiter super legitur,
                        scribere rogaverunt. Signa manuum <persName key="#Viscount"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/104">Rugeri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs> filii <persName>Ildebrandi</persName>
                        et <persName>Wlpelli</persName> filii [<persName>Perli</persName>] et
                            <persName>Berardini</persName> filii <persName>Petri Grassi</persName>
                        et <persName>Malpilli</persName> filii eius et <persName>Raineri</persName>
                        filii <persName>Rufinelli</persName> et <persName>Tancredi</persName> filii
                            <persName>Ugiccionis Berardoni</persName> et
                            <persName>Salarii</persName> filii <persName>Walfredi</persName> da
                            <placeName>Tremali</placeName> et <persName>Wazonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Monteliverenti</placeName> et <persName>Widonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Monticulo</placeName>. Confirmatum est hoc a comitissa
                        Maximilla in <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/88"
                            >Malliano</placeName>, testibus Widone de Monticulo et
                            <persName>Rugeri</persName> et <persName>Banbarini</persName>. Ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Judge">Agimerigus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni
                        imperatoris post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
